{"tid":355600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞左個Kickstarter Campaign, 你問我答","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:31.000Z","uid":123803,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"335f103880e1efcc55c2520d0b501d76342399a6","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"最近搞左個Kickstarter Campaign, 都叫做籌到下錢咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩問題都可以問下，例如搞之前做過啲咩，搞嗰陣有咩困難嗰啲。<br />\n<br />\n其實出呢個post都係想借個機會宣傳下(<a href=\"http://orii.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forii.io&d=ZnMbo5WqFQ2J4nKTDIlH0UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f58aa421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">orii.io</a>) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144ffdf0f3f745b2fa11bfebfb04dc4ac95111c4","tid":355600,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"恭喜巴打<br />\n向成功量產邁出重要一步<br />\n<br />\n請問條片拍咗幾錢？揾邊間幫你拍？<br />\n有冇賣廣告？<br />\n<br />\n仲有你用美國 account?"},{"pid":"0021e21e10ec788eddde300a072724f71140b01c","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭喜巴打<br />\n向成功量產邁出重要一步<br />\n<br />\n請問條片拍咗幾錢？揾邊間幫你拍？<br />\n有冇賣廣告？<br />\n<br />\n仲有你用美國 account?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵咗個friend 拍同埋剪，加埋租器材要四萬幾蚊。<br />\nScript 係成班同事一齊寫，演員都係啲同事同埋朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有喺facebook 落廣告<br />\n<br />\n係用美國account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849092a5df9fce15bfcd2f9fe5987d5fba6b8c12","tid":355600,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個product由構思到成形籌備左幾耐？<br />\ninvestment大概有幾多？<br />\n成team有幾多人同分別負責咩task?<br />\n之前有冇相關經驗先敢開始呢個project?<br />\nproject途中遇到最大困難係咩？<br />\n今次超晒標，下一步有咩大計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝分享先<br />\n學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649031e48c0040eac15fec75897166d694033d37","tid":355600,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"btw試用個part第二條女好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f794d49adff5b573258aae2ad825a238275d168c","tid":355600,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d411f878c96c688c7fe38bed3d27fca32bae2fbe","tid":355600,"uid":21480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fed9575116bb2b7f3aafec54bdc6b2ad68def03a","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個product由構思到成形籌備左幾耐？<br />\ninvestment大概有幾多？<br />\n成team有幾多人同分別負責咩task?<br />\n之前有冇相關經驗先敢開始呢個project?<br />\nproject途中遇到最大困難係咩？<br />\n今次超晒標，下一步有咩大計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝分享先<br />\n學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一開始係因為有個同事嘅老竇細細個就盲咗。<br />\n咁宜加啲電話成個芒都係平嘅，啲盲人根本就觸摸唔到（voice interface)。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢就想整啲嘢幫到佢地更加方便咁用電話（voice interface)，咁由一開始拼湊啲耳機同手帶， 到之後變成一隻戒指，再宜加嘅設計，中間都經過咗十七款, 用左年半左右。<br />\n<br />\ninvestment 加埋比賽獎金就有大概50萬美金，都係一路做r&amp;d (research and development)，一路參加比賽同埋用啲prototype 去吸引投資者去投資。<br />\n<br />\n成team 一開始就有四個人，都係科大同學，次後到宜加，計埋啲intern 有12個人，分別係做operation, marketing, hardware 同埋software development.<br />\n<br />\n一開始四個人都無乜由零開始整產品嘅經驗, 有啲本身讀政治，有啲本身喺讀public health咁樣。 初頭都係去鴨暸街買啲電線，拼拼湊凑，搵啲friend 做3d print 個case 出黎，去到之後搵到投資者，有錢去搵人做產品設計，用啲好啲嘅物料，去到宜加有個fully functional prototype.<br />\n<br />\n最大嘅困難係啲人未試過係好難會知道你件產品係咩嚟， 所以都係不停咁去啲展覽，不停搵人去試，去建立一個信呢件產品既群體。<br />\n<br />\n嚟近除咗係量產同送貨之外，宜加都係發堀下喺其他市場（eg. 德國，日本) 既可能性，同埋keep 住software 嘅發展咁樣。"},{"pid":"6767b3e8a74739d87d5094577c2dd241d9e618bb","tid":355600,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"好似幾撚勁"},{"pid":"da45af7e9432edf5552982dc66e6fc517a657126","tid":355600,"uid":61844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"Keep住update個app，改善用家體驗呢方面好重要 祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfae25ae6ee2ef393275c21adce47f2035f51d1","tid":355600,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對比之下 搞風扇嗰個真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望佢唔好睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f005052e3c1eda056174ba6d49c34f4e4acbbad","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Keep住update個app，改善用家體驗呢方面好重要 祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜加同一間software 公司一齊搞緊個app，希望送貨之前可以搞靚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6417fc5a760c01cc6ed0accda49a73ab1a440261","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個product由構思到成形籌備左幾耐？<br />\ninvestment大概有幾多？<br />\n成team有幾多人同分別負責咩task?<br />\n之前有冇相關經驗先敢開始呢個project?<br />\nproject途中遇到最大困難係咩？<br />\n今次超晒標，下一步有咩大計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝分享先<br />\n學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一開始係因為有個同事嘅老竇細細個就盲咗。<br />\n咁宜加啲電話成個芒都係平嘅，啲盲人根本就觸摸唔到（<span style=\"color: red;\">screen</span> interface)。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢就想整啲嘢幫到佢地更加方便咁用電話（voice interface)，咁由一開始拼湊啲耳機同手帶， 到之後變成一隻戒指，再宜加嘅設計，中間都經過咗十七款, 用左年半左右。<br />\n<br />\ninvestment 加埋比賽獎金就有大概50萬美金，都係一路做r&amp;d (research and development)，一路參加比賽同埋用啲prototype 去吸引投資者去投資。<br />\n<br />\n成team 一開始就有四個人，都係科大同學，次後到宜加，計埋啲intern 有12個人，分別係做operation, marketing, hardware 同埋software development.<br />\n<br />\n一開始四個人都無乜由零開始整產品嘅經驗, 有啲本身讀政治，有啲本身喺讀public health咁樣。 初頭都係去鴨暸街買啲電線，拼拼湊凑，搵啲friend 做3d print 個case 出黎，去到之後搵到投資者，有錢去搵人做產品設計，用啲好啲嘅物料，去到宜加有個fully functional prototype.<br />\n<br />\n最大嘅困難係啲人未試過係好難會知道你件產品係咩嚟， 所以都係不停咁去啲展覽，不停搵人去試，去建立一個信呢件產品既群體。<br />\n<br />\n嚟近除咗係量產同送貨之外，宜加都係發堀下喺其他市場（eg. 德國，日本) 既可能性，同埋keep 住software 嘅發展咁樣。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41bd67b2146ec6714bd875bb2610542e87a99a7","tid":355600,"uid":65408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"原來呢個campaign係香港人搞嘅，我見好多網站都有介紹，真係覺得呢個idea好正。祝你賺多啲眼球吸引多d投資者。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好成為下個咖啡機騙案！"},{"pid":"8a34a632117013957280819014551f6a99435808","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來呢個campaign係香港人搞嘅，我見好多網站都有介紹，真係覺得呢個idea好正。祝你賺多啲眼球吸引多d投資者。<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好成為下個咖啡機騙案！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝哂!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實喺香港kickstarter 個朵都臭哂<br />\n個個一聽到Kickstarter 就會話你cap 水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為個朵臭到咁，我地係搞campaign 之前已經整咗個fully functional 嘅prototype, 證明俾人睇我地其實已經七七八八，係差同間廠落訂㗎啫， 都想話番俾人知香港Kickstarter 其實仲有好多有心做嘅人。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣想喺上面搞project，我都可以分享下啲心得㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23054b8018e6eb5d9577c3ef616416e10519a003","tid":355600,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對比之下 搞風扇嗰個真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3184d755df41810043f3aec13111ad403bae6b61","tid":355600,"uid":123803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似幾撚勁</blockquote><br />\n多謝爸打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}